<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_87_r3l34">Wir ~ die <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . deʒ Rats <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> etc <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc / Als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> erber vnd veſte Balthaſar </ab>
