<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> dez rats
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> etc.,
                                                  <expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc., als
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> erber und veste
                                                Balthasar von Wenkheim
                                                  <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> het
                                                  <expan>F<ex>ritz</ex></expan> Scheffer und
                                                  <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, seinen sun, dez
                                                  <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Lantmans,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, knechte,
                                                die er <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ledig gelassen
                                                hat, als uns <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> gesagt und
                                                  <expan>gepete<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, daz wir
                                                darumb des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Wenkheim frewnd
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wir
                                                  <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Balthasars von
                                                  <expan>Wenkh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>helff<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> der, die
                                                  <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> sind, güt frewnd
                                                umb die tat
                                                  <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>l<ex>ich</ex></expan>. Mit
                                                  <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
